Dec 2022 • Couples
Golden bridge is iconic bridge of Vietnam.it’s man made engineering marvel, must visit place.The bridge is designed in the way that it looks like ,it is supported by two hands . We went to bana hills in the month of December. The ropeway to the top is one of the longest in the world,5 km long. The weather was not good, it was totally covered by clouds and raining through out our visit.so we were wearing woollens and raincoat,carrying umbrella with us.the sun world is also good place to hangout and take different rides and shows.
